msgid "Using *RStudio*: A (very) brief guide!"
msgstr ""

#: ../../trainings/training3/03_using_rstudio.rst:4
msgid ""
"Now that you have both *R* and *RStudio* installed on your computer, you can "
"begin using and interacting with *R* by opening the *RStudio* program. Open "
"*RStudio* just as you would any program, by clicking on its icon (if you "
"created a Desktop shortcut) or by searching for “RStudio” in your *Menu* of "
"installed programs (in Windows this would be your *Start Menu*)."
msgstr ""

