msgstr ""

#: ../../trainings/training3/03_using_rstudio.rst:14
msgid "Plots, Files, Packages, Help, Viewer, etc. (bottom right)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../trainings/training3/03_using_rstudio.rst:21
msgid ""
"Each pane can be minimized or maximized within its column by clicking the "
"minimize/maximize buttons - you can also see if a pane is collapsed (and not "
"visible) in this way."
msgstr ""

#: ../../trainings/training3/03_using_rstudio.rst:24
msgid "Customising the Layout"
msgstr ""

#: ../../trainings/training3/03_using_rstudio.rst:26
msgid ""
"You can change the layout of the panes, and their arrangement, to something "
"you prefer by modifying these setting within **Tools → Global Options → Pane "
"Layout** (Linux Mint)."
